#
# üí∞ RISK MANAGEMENT:
# - Conservative: Lower target percentages, tighter stop losses
# - Aggressive: Higher target percentages, wider stop losses
# - Tier A should always have best risk/reward ratios
#
# üíº PAPER TRADING:
# - Start with smaller amounts ($25-50 per trade) to test strategies
# - Increase trade amounts as you gain confidence
# - Monitor performance over 100+ trades before going live
#
# ‚è∞ TIMING OPTIMIZATION:
# - Bull market: Decrease SCAN_INTERVAL_MINUTES (more frequent scanning)
# - Bear market: Increase SCAN_INTERVAL_MINUTES (less noise)
# - High volatility: Tighter stop losses, quicker targets
#
# üìä PERFORMANCE TUNING:
